13
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,480
What?

14
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,400
I remember your original business philosophy, brother:

15
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,560
to provide the public with

16
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,820
affordable yet high-quality products,

17
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:34,720
winning through value for money.

18
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,920
But from the looks of it,

19
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:37,600
our company is changing direction.

20
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,640
Do you also think there's something wrong with this contract?

21
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,039
I can't quite put my finger on it,

22
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:42,440
but something feels off,

23
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,080
though I can't explain why.

24
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:45,610
Have you seen the contract?

25
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,479
No, I haven't,

26
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:50,610
and Second Brother wouldn't show it to me anyway.

27
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,240
I understand.

28
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,520
I'll figure something out.

29
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:56,400
Alright, brother. I'll be going then.

30
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,729
I just wanted to check on you before I left.

31
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:06,720
Jin Daxi, we're switching shifts tonight.

32
