33
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,260
Working overtime.

34
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,960
That looks complicated.

35
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,970
Snow Leopard Group?

36
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,200
