123
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:02,640
This is my investigation result on Qimingxing Company.

124
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:04,520
Qimingxing Company is nothing but

125
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:06,040
a shell company with no actual

126
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,440
production whatsoever.

127
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,440
The contract everyone has seen

128
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:10,100
is just an external contract.

129
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,530
While this one in my hand

130
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:13,370
is the real internal contract.

131
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:14,810
Give me a moment.

132
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,240
I've checked,

133
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,480
you've been in charge of the contracts all along.

134
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,440
I also know that day

135
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,440
you were going to submit the final contract.

136
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,760
So I pretended to run into you

137
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:24,220
and have dinner together.

138
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:27,320
I've already sent the content to everyone's phones.

139
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,780
Everyone can check it now.

140
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:31,840
These are dual contracts.

141
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:32,640
That's right,

142
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,960
